    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="千秋岁·数声鶗鴂"><a href="#千秋岁·数声鶗鴂" class="headerlink" title="千秋岁·数声鶗鴂"></a><center>千秋岁·数声鶗鴂</center></h1><p><strong><center>[北宋]张先</center></strong></p><center>数声鶗鴂，又报芳菲歇。</center><center>惜春更把残红折。</center><center>雨轻风色暴，梅子青时节。</center><center>永丰柳，</center><center>无人尽日花飞雪。</center></br><center>莫把幺弦拨，怨极弦能说。</center><center>天不老，情难绝。</center><center>心似双丝网，中有千千结。</center><center>夜过也，</center><center>东窗未白凝残月。</center><span id="more"></span><style>    /* 楷体 */  /* 只设置 markdown 字体 */  .markdown-body {    font-family: KaiTi,"Microsoft YaHei",Georgia, sans, serif;    font-size: 20px;  }</style>]]></content>
    
    
