    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="苏幕遮·草"><a href="#苏幕遮·草" class="headerlink" title="苏幕遮·草"></a><center>苏幕遮·草</center></h1><p><strong><center>[北宋]梅尧臣</center></strong></p><center>露堤平，烟墅杳。乱碧萋萋，雨后江天晓。</center><center>独有庾郎年最少。窣地春袍，嫩色宜相照。</center></br><center>接长亭，迷远道。堪怨王孙，不记归期早。</center><center>落尽梨花春又了。满地残阳，翠色和烟老。</center><span id="more"></span><div class="note note-success">            <p>曲水飘香去不归，梨花落尽成秋苑。 ——李贺《三月》</p>          </div><style>    /* 楷体 */  /* 只设置 markdown 字体 */  .markdown-body {    font-family: KaiTi,"Microsoft YaHei",Georgia, sans, serif;    font-size: 20px;  }</style>]]></content>
    
    
