    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="丑奴儿·书博山道中壁"><a href="#丑奴儿·书博山道中壁" class="headerlink" title="丑奴儿·书博山道中壁"></a><center>丑奴儿·书博山道中壁</center></h1><p><strong><center>[南宋]辛弃疾</center></strong></p><center>少年不识愁滋味，爱上层楼。</center><center>爱上层楼，为赋新词强说愁。</center></br><center>而今识尽愁滋味，欲说还休。</center><center>欲说还休，却道天凉好个秋。</center><span id="more"></span><style>    /* 楷体 */  /* 只设置 markdown 字体 */  .markdown-body {    font-family: KaiTi,"Microsoft YaHei",Georgia, sans, serif;    font-size: 20px;  }</style>]]></content>
    
    
